-- Apple Computer Planning to Open `Many' New Stores in China After Shanghai
-- Mark Lee
-- 2010-07-08T03:33:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-08/apple-computer-planning-to-open-many-new-stores-in-china-after-shanghai.html

          
          
             Apple Inc.’s Shanghai store that’s
opening in two days will be among the “many” new stores the
company is planning to have in the country, the company said in
a statement today.  
